recipes.name: Wiener Schnitzel
instructions: Pound veal cutlets thin
Dredge in flour, egg, then breadcrumbs
Fry in butter until golden brown
Drain on paper towels
Serve immediately with lemon wedges
Accompany with parsley potatoes
